openfreebuds (0.10-1) impish; urgency=medium

  * New: integrated mmk_updater
  * New: cli-actions can be used without running app
  * UI: new tkinter-based settings ui
  * UI: reduced size of tray menu
  * UI: added debug features
  * UI: handle ctrl-c for safe exit
  * Manager: HONOR Earbuds 2 Lite marked as supported
  * Manager: use Bluetooth SDP instead of hard-coded port number
  * Device: added long tap configuration
  * Device: use group-organized props
  * Device: use python arrays instead of lists
  * Windows installer: kill app on update/reinstall
  * Misc: removed psutil dependency
  * Misc: xlib become optional

 -- MelianMiko <melianmiko@gmail.com>  Wed, 02 Mar 2022 19:33:30 +0700
